name: Kirriwani Leth
description:
A 1/1 piece from the upcoming sci-fi fantasy Graphic Novel series, veil of the gods - coming soon. This is one of the characters from the series. 

Kirriwani Leth is an upgraded high end Kwasi that has original parts of her deceased 
prototype incorporated into her system. She is the first generation of truly bio-mimetic 
Kwasis. However, as she has discovered, being constructed from the finest technology 
available isn’t necessarily a recipe for happiness.
